{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1780128182229,"sessionID":"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"webfetch","callID":"call_function_d9o8ac6jmgq3_1","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"url":"https://browse.ai"},"output":"Scrape and Monitor Data from Any Website with No Code - Browse AI           \n\n \n\n[\n\n![Browse AI Logo](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/68b9c3f45cf94ad7aa6e4c18_1.1%20Primary%20Logo_Default.png)\n\n](https://www.browse.ai)\n\nFeatures\n\nFeatures\n\n[\n\nAI web scraper\n\nScrape data from any website with no code.\n\n\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/extract)[\n\nWebsites to spreadsheets\n\nTurn websites into live spreadsheets in Google Sheets or Airtable.\n\n\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/website-to-spreadsheet)[\n\nWebsite monitoring\n\nAI change detection and monitoring.\n\n\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/monitor)[\n\n7,000+ Integrations\n\nIntegrate your data with almost any app or tool in a few clicks.\n\n\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/integrations)[\n\nWebsites to APIs\n\nTurn any websites into an API in minutes.\n\n\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/website-to-api)[\n\nWeb scraping services\n\nFully managed web scraping and monitoring solutions.\n\n\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/managed-web-scraping)[\n\n250+ Prebuilt robots\n\nAutomatically extract data from top websites.\n\n\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/prebuilt-robots)\n\nPlatform Overview\n\n![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/687a4a92ac57a8731c4a3897/6932ee6791f3c620261e1ff6_RS-Mockup-1.png)\n\nExtract data from your first website for free\n\nScrape and monitor data on the best AI scraping platform. No coding required.\n\n[\n\nSign up\n\n](https://dashboard.browse.ai/signup)\n\nUse cases\n\nBy data category\n\n[\n\nPrice monitoring\n\nMonitor prices and products from any website reliably with no code.\n\n\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/use-cases/price-monitoring)[\n\nE-Commerce\n\nReliably scrape and monitor product data, competitors, and vendors at scale.\n\n\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/use-cases/scraping-ecommerce)[\n\nReal estate data\n\nScrape property listings, pricing, market data, and more from the top real estate sites.\n\n\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/use-cases/scrape-real-estate-data)[\n\nJob listings\n\nScrape and monitor job listings, candidates, and more across multiple platforms and websites.\n\n\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/use-cases/industry-recruitment)[\n\nLegal data\n\nExtract and monitor legal data including case data, scraping laws, judgements, and more.\n\n\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/use-cases/law-firm)[\n\nLead generation\n\nTurn any website into your lead generation engine with automated data extraction.\n\n\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/use-cases/lead-generation)[\n\nExtract data for LLMs\n\nExtract data from any website and sync it with your LLM of choice.\n\n\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/use-cases/llm-scraping)[\n\nExplore all use cases\n\nFind out how {{userCount}}+ users have scraped and monitored web data at scale.\n\n\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/use-cases)\n\nResources\n\nResources\n\n[\n\nBlog\n\nNews, articles & tutorials. Updated weekly.\n\n\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/blog)[\n\nTalk to sales\n\nDiscuss your web scraping projects with our experts.\n\n\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/service)[\n\nHelp center\n\nGet quick answers to your questions.\n\n\n\n](https://help.browse.ai)[\n\nAbout Browse AI\n\nLearn more about Browse AI's story.\n\n\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/about-us)[\n\nAPI documentation\n\nIntegrate with, or build apps on top of Browse AI.\n\n\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/docs/api/v2)[\n\nAffiliate program\n\nGet 20% commission for every subscriber you refer. Forever!\n\n\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/affiliate-program)\n\n![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/68b9c3f49ec1d2611adb5cab_3D%20Robot_Default.png)\n\nBook a consultation call\n\nIf you’re looking for:\n\n-   Dedicated web scraping services\n-   Customized data post processing and management\n-   Have a complex use case\n-   Have a highly scaled use case\n\n…we’d love to talk to you to learn more about your needs.\n\n[\n\nBook a call with sales\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/service)\n\n[Pricing](https://www.browse.ai/pricing)\n\n[\n\nLog in\n\n](https://dashboard.browse.ai/login)[\n\nLogin\n\n](https://dashboard.browse.ai/login)[\n\nGet started for free\n\n](https://dashboard.browse.ai/signup)\n\nSimple data scraping.\n\n# Scrape and monitor data from any website reliably at scale  \n\nTransform any website into a live data pipeline with the leading AI-powered data extraction platform.  \n\nRated **4.9** by\n\n  \n\n[\n\nGet started for free\n\n](https://dashboard.browse.ai/signup)[\n\nBook a consultation call\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/service)\n\n![Zapier logo](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/678031b4f27bc0fe3526b15b_download%20(1)%201.png)![Google logo](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/678031b481f9ad5db586919e_google%201.png)![METRO logo](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/678031b4bd374cb94baefa61_company%20logo2.png)![Salesforce logo](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/678031b48fee9150b823ca50_salesforce-logo-b4913d568a5a237bf25580370192582c%201.png)![Amazon logo](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/678031b4ccd6a542e27e9096_amazon-logo-c23f8661a28b85fa54d6f4a268adad1f%201.png)![RE/MAX logo](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/678031b4e6b1c44f06a3a7f3_company%20logo8%201.png)![Ray White logo](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/678031b42b8611985096fe03_company%20logo1.png)\n\n## The #1 AI web scraper and monitoring platform\n\nBrowse AI is the leading data scraper that provides reliable data for over {{userCount}} users worldwide helping them scrape, monitor, and integrate data from almost any website with no coding required.\n\n### Build your AI web scraper or monitor with no code\n\nPoint and click to extract, scrape, and monitor any data on any webpage.  \n  \n[Learn more ->](https://www.browse.ai/extract)  \n\n### Monitor for website changes\n\nAI web scraper and monitoring tool that alerts you to website changes and automatically adapts so the code doesn't break.  \n  \n[Learn more ->](https://www.browse.ai/monitor)  \n\n### Export, integrate or connect\n\n[Transform web data into an API](https://www.browse.ai/website-to-api) or Webook or integrate scraped data with 7,000+ tools and apps to build automated workflows.  \n  \n[Learn more ->](https://www.browse.ai/integrations)  \n\n### Extract data from any website\n\nAI website scraper with dynamic content capture, built-in bot evasion, proxy management, automatic retries, and rate limiting.  \n  \n[Learn more ->](https://www.browse.ai/extract)  \n\n### Extract data from thousands of webpages\n\nThe most reliable AI web scraper on the market, built on a platform designed for limitless scale.  \n  \n[Learn more ->](https://www.browse.ai/extract)  \n\n### Web scraping services\n\nWeb data scraping services and web monitoring solutions for enterprise web scraping and monitoring.  \n  \n[Learn more ->](https://www.browse.ai/managed-web-scraping)  \n\n## Transform any website into a reliable data pipeline at scale (no coding required)\n\nScrape, monitor, and integrate data from any website using our AI-powered data extraction platform.\n\nWeb scraper\n\nMonitoring\n\nAI-powered\n\nWorkflows\n\nAutomations\n\nIntegrations\n\n![Browse AI web scraper data extraction interface](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/68d58b24599aa27b10983ee0_AI%20scraper.png)\n\n![Browse AI website monitoring dashboard](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/68d58dbc62c85d05eff81b0f_web-page-monitoring.png)\n\n![Browse AI AI-powered intelligent data extraction](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/68d58de99f220e21f43c34e2_intelligent.png)\n\n![Browse AI automated data workflows](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/68d58e087fe7d0d91dec8bd0_AI%20scraper.png)\n\n![Browse AI task automation and scheduling](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/68d58e4396742140cdaad765_automations.png)\n\n![Browse AI third-party app integrations](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/68d58e67543c479dbab31c75_integrations.png)\n\n \n\n## Easy, reliable, and scalable data extraction, web scraping, and  website monitoring.\n\n### AI website scraper designed for data accuracy\n\nExtract and monitor the data you need reliability with automated site layout monitoring, human behavior emulation, and geo-based data extraction.\n\n![Extracted data results table showing web scraping output](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/66f70927dbc7563e729818f5_Table.png)![Browse AI, AI assistant](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/66edfed8d2c53b8e1eaf2ce6_Group%20576.png)\n\nIs this the data you were looking for?\n\nYes, Looks Perfect\n\nNo, Try Again\n\n### Extract data from thousands of web pages\n\nCreate your first web scraper or web monitor in minutes on a platform designed to capture billions of data records.\n\n![Browse AI at scale](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/6707543eb9b1b98e0f3df31b_Steps%20(2).png)![Large-scale data extraction from thousands of web pages](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/66f7096df046f1da932a8c6b_Frame%2012903%20(1).png)\n\n### Scrape and monitor entire websites with deep scraping\n\nAutomate data extraction from pages and subpages with workflows and automations.\n\n![Browse AI deep scraping](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/6707530587f1e0f555f7e917_Frame%2012584%20(1).png)![Deep scraping across website pages and subpages](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/6707fc17963388a622ad2eef_Frame%2012584%20(2).png)\n\n### Monitor websites for changes automatically\n\nSchedule data extraction, web scrapers, and webpage monitors to run hourly, daily, weekly, or monthly to check for changes.\n\n![Browse AI Monitor](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/66f2177bac2f30b7f7027c69_Frame%2012867.svg)![Website content change detection and monitoring](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/66f7086965c0549639503cca_Content.png)\n\n### Smart human-like data extraction\n\nMimics human actions on the page to scrape dynamic content including drop downs, search bars, form fills, and more.\n\n![Browse AI captcha](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/670755fa2ebe6b5ccb31bbf7_Frame%2012574.png)![Human-like browser interaction for smart data extraction](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/67075fc3d04cfd38a1fae07d_Frame%2012573%20(1).png)\n\nThe AI web scraper and web monitoring platform trusted by thousands of businesses worldwide.\n\n![Amazon logo](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/670ee4904047e968aeb3fdd3_Frame%2012603.png)\n\n![Salesforce logo](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/66bcf69f8fbd19ca1bd911c8_salesforce-logo-b4913d568a5a237bf25580370192582c.svg)\n\n![HubSpot logo](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/66bcf69fde40b67c3ad47143_download%20(1).svg)\n\n![RE/MAX logo](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/66bcf69fa12c80be7d47d035_download.svg)\n\n![Accenture logo](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/66bcf69f8b66601b7b762eec_accenture-logo-cc2c67c1d1275b8fed546c335260decc.svg)\n\n![Klue logo](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/66bcf69ec6c2c023a364dd4b_download%20(5).svg)\n\n![Zapier logo](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/66bcf69e6f23a2272b256c08_download%20(2).svg)\n\n![METRO logo](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/670ee45fef3ce1770b842f9c_Frame%2012606.png)\n\n![Ray White logo](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/670ee47198f8c40745718022_Frame%2012613.png)\n\nEnterprise Web Scraping\n\n## Fully managed web scraping services\n\nEnd-to-end data extraction services fully supported by our web scraping services team.\n\n### Web scraping services\n\nGet the data you need, structured how you want it, into the system you need it in with zero hassle or technical lift with our data extraction services.\n\n### Enterprise web scraping\n\nPowered by Browse AI’s data extraction platform to ensure reliability and scalability. \n\n### Web scraping solutions\n\nData extraction services and web data scraping services customized to your needs - we scrape, format, and send you the data you need.\n\n![G2 Easiest Admin badge for Data Extraction](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/67634d0f5c3dae38cccea228_DataExtraction_EasiestAdmin_EaseOfAdmin.svg)![G2 High Performer badge for Data Extraction](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/67634d0f3b149ec9637c8c75_DataExtraction_HighPerformer_HighPerformer.svg)![G2 Small Business Leader badge for Data Extraction](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/67634d0fa33ce67e797f2c37_DataExtraction_Leader_Small-Business_Leader.svg)![G2 Momentum Leader badge for Data Extraction](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/67634d0f6924a99f1d028a57_DataExtraction_MomentumLeader_Leader.svg)\n\n[\n\nTalk to sales ->\n\n](https://www.browse.ai/managed-web-scraping)\n\n![Security shield icon](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/687a4a92ac57a8731c4a3897/68cd6a16c7723bfc76c482c1_shield-tick.svg)\n\nEnterprise-grade security and compliance\n\nYour scraped and monitored data is protected by enterprise level security and compliance standards.\n\nSOC 2 Type II certified\n\nIndependently audited security controls.\n\nGDPR compliant\n\nFull data privacy and protection.\n\nEncrypted data transfer\n\nTLS 1.3 encryption for all data movement.\n\nRole-based access control\n\nGranular permissions for team members.\n\nData retention policies\n\nAutomatic cleanup based on your requirements.\n\nDedicated infrastructure\n\nIsolated environments for enterprise clients.\n\n## The most scalable, reliable, and adaptable web scraping platform and web monitoring tool on the market.\n\n480,000+\n\nRows of extracted web data\n\n250,000+\n\nTask Automated\n\n250,000+\n\nHours Saved\n\n![Photo of Taylor M., CEO](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/66f6f9509a2e065d72dcb3e1_taylor-85179050c306c8b27ff423d42c7cdf4a.jpg)\n\nTaylor M.\n\nCEO\n\nBrowse AI has been immensely helpful as it enabled us to **scrape live inventory** data from our retailers that they are unwilling to provide to new vendors. This means my sales team knows who to call and when and saves immeasurable time. 10/10.  \n\nEasy to Use\n\nEasy to Use\n\n![Photo of Chris C., Partner Development Specialist](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/66bcf28f2b77757c47c1a972_thumb_square_31a77a02cb2eaac8f4563f33c8ac10f2.webp)\n\nChris C.  \n\nPartner Development Specialist\n\nThe UX is all point-and-click, and it's incredibly easy to integrate with whatever automation or database you want to use. Everything is no-code, so as a non-technical person **I felt empowered** to be able to do anything I needed with a bit of learning and testing.  \n\nEasy to Use\n\nEasy to Use\n\n![Photo of Yassine B., Multidisciplinary Designer](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/66bcf33cea8623c494844081_Yassine.webp)\n\nYassine B.\n\nMultidisciplinary Designer\n\nHow easy it is to setup a scraper! just set and forget with the monitor. **Fastest customer support I've witnessed**. They even helped me with a Robot I set up which had to scrape data behind some firewall.  \n\nEasy to Use\n\nEasy to Use\n\n![Photo of Holden T., Director](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/66f6f716171fc1eb2b6da9a2_holden.jpg)\n\nHolden T.\n\nDirector\n\nBrowse AI simplified the process of scraping websites for basic data and being able to rapidly grab data from a variety of sources. We've used many related tools in the past and **Browse AI is by far the most powerful** and easiest to use to date.  \n\nEasy to Use\n\nEasy to Use\n\n![Photo of Erin J.](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/66bcf3df483ed7855e887153_erin.avif)\n\nErin J.  \n\nIt's so easy to follow along and teach it to do the work for you. **Even a complete beginner** can build a working tool super quickly. Building these used to take hours now it takes minutes with Browse AI.  \n\nEasy to Use\n\nEasy to Use\n\n![Photo of Mauricio A.](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/66bcf4ea8413e1ad068356c4_mauricio.webp)\n\nMauricio A.  \n\nIt’s a very simply and reliable tool to extract data from web. **In just minutes I solved my problems** with Browse AI after spending hours with other tools.  \n\nEasy to Use\n\nEasy to Use\n\n![Photo of Jonathan G., CTO](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/66bcf2cfdaada21aa64f22c6_Jonathan.jpg)\n\nJonathan G.  \n\nCTO\n\nBrowse AI is fabulous and has **saved us many many days of development time** allowing us to focus on the core features of our platform rather than data capture. Customer Support has always been super responsive and very very helpful. I strongly recommend Browse AI to anyone who needs to implement web data capture for their project.  \n\nEasy to Use\n\nNo-Code\n\n![Photo of Martin T., Senior Consultant](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/640f57f0e5c685703cf11249_thumb_square_91ab6ef28cfff3e2325fa554e2796db5.webp)\n\nMartin T.\n\nSenior Consultant - Business automation\n\nBrowse AI's **Great REST API connections** make it easy for me to use the information captured in a workflow - or post it into a database.  \n\nEasy to Use\n\nEasy to Use\n\n![Photo of Rukaiya B.](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628be7c04ab34bfc699e4acb/66bcf381b33663aa4ea13030_rukaiya.jpg)\n\nRukaiya B.  \n\nBrowse AI allows you to scrape websites with no code and is **so simple and easy to use**. You can scrape absolutely any website using this without any hustle and download the results too.  \n\nEasy to Use\n\nEasy to Use\n\n \n\n## Jumpstart your web scraping with 200+ prebuilt robots\n\nPrebuilt web scrapers and web monitors you can get started in two clicks.\n\nE-Commerce\n\nReal estate\n\nRecruiting\n\nSocial media\n\nSearch engine\n\nDigital publishing\n\nMarket research\n\nTechnology\n\n![Amazon](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6321fa2dbaaf1d18927bc80e/671293f7675bb0d2c5024173_4aed1c6c-a98c-4448-9108-f0ebd1499944_amazon%2540full.avif)\n\n[Amazon Canada price tracker and search results monitor](/t/monitor-amazon-ca-search-results)\n\nTrack Amazon Canada search results for price changes, ranking positions, and sponsored listings. No coding. Start free.\n\n[Check Details ->](/t/monitor-amazon-ca-search-results)\n\n![Amazon](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6321fa2dbaaf1d18927bc80e/671293f7675bb0d2c5024173_4aed1c6c-a98c-4448-9108-f0ebd1499944_amazon%2540full.avif)\n\n[Amazon keyword rank tracker and search results scraper](/t/scrape-amazon-us-search-results)\n\nTrack Amazon keyword rankings and scrape search results with position, product link, image, price, rating, reviews, and sponsored vs organic status. No code required.\n\n[Check Details ->](/t/scrape-amazon-us-search-results)\n\n![Amazon](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6321fa2dbaaf1d18927bc80e/671293f7675bb0d2c5024173_4aed1c6c-a98c-4448-9108-f0ebd1499944_amazon%2540full.avif)\n\n[Amazon search results scraper for any search URL](/t/scrape-amazon-search-results-via-url)\n\nScrape Amazon search results from any URL for product position, title, link, image, price, rating, reviews, and sponsored status. No coding. Start free.\n\n[Check Details ->